 <!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title> Cats Gallery </title>
		<link rel="stylesheet"  href="css/style.css" />	
	</head>
	<body>
	<section id="how-can-i-help">
        <h2>How can I help?</h2>
        <div class="d-flex">
          <div class="adoption">
            <h1 class="adoptionHeader">Adoption</h1>
            <img class="adoptionImg" src="img/HowCanI3.webp" />
            <div class="adoptionText">
              "When considering adopting a new buddy, some things should be
              considered in advanced (such as age, gender,...ect). That is why
              we always recommend to ask us any doubt or questions as well as
              doing some researchs of
              <a
                href="https://www.thesprucepets.com/top-mistakes-of-cat-owners-555300"
                target="_blank"
              >
                things to avoid as a cat owner.</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="fostering">
            <h1 class="fosteringHeader">Fostering</h1>
            <img class="fosteringImg" src="img/HowCanIHelp2.webp" />
            <div class="fosteringText">
              "Reliable owners are vital to getting cats to fit in perfectly.
              Finding committed people allows us to help abandoned, lost cats
              that would otherwise struggle to survive in harsh conditions. We
              offer 24/7 support to make you able to give the warmest
              <a
                href="https://www.cats.org.uk/adopt-a-cat/preparing-for-a-cat"
                target="_blank"
              >
                welcome to your cat
              </a>

              ."
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="volunteering">
            <h1 class="volunteeringHeader">Volunteer</h1>
            <img class="volunteeringImg" src="img/HowCanIHelp1.webp" />
            <div class="volunteeringText">
              "<b>Java The Cat </b>is looking for people who is willing to help
              us with fostering, transport, adopting, or volunteer events. If
              you are interested in being part of our team, please fill the
              contact form to know our current volunteer roles. We will contact
              you in no time!."
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button class="donate-button">Donate</button>
      </section>
      <br />
      <br />
	  </body>
</html>